-- Kuoni Plans Share Sale in Mumbai for Part of Its Visa Unit, NZZ Reports
-- Elena Logutenkova
-- 2010-08-01T10:44:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-01/kuoni-plans-share-sale-in-mumbai-for-part-of-its-visa-unit-nzz-reports.html

          
          
             Kuoni Reisen Holding AG  is planning
to sell part of its visa-facilitation unit VFS Global through an
initial public offering in Mumbai in autumn,  NZZ am Sonntag 
reported, citing unidentified people familiar with the matter.  
 The company may sell a quarter of the unit, NZZ reported. A
Kuoni spokesman told the newspaper it doesnâ€™t comment on rumors.  
